Package: gwasvcf
Title: Tools for Dealing with GWAS Summary Data in VCF Format
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gibran", "Hemani", , "g.hemani@bristol.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0920-1055"))
Description: Tools for dealing with GWAS summary data in VCF format.
    The package includes functions for reading, querying, and writing the VCF 
    format. It also includes helper functions such for performing LD proxy 
    searches.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/mrcieu/gwasvcf
